$ Windows subsystem

{ Important components #subsystem-windows-components

  The following → Windows/development/Portable-Executable/DLL[dlls] implement crticial functionality for the Windows subsystem:
    • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/basesrv_dll[basesrv.dll]
    • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/csrsrv_dll[csrsrv.dll]
    • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/sxssrv_dll[sxssrv.dll]
    • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/winsrv_dll[winsrv.dll]

  These DLLs are loaded by → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/csrss_exe[`csrss.exe`] and
  are responsible for handling mouse and keyoboard input, housekeeping, terminating → Windows/development/process[processes] (`ExitWindowsEx`), Side-by-Side (SxS) fustion and manifest cache support etc.

}
